This repository currently contains original shader approximations shaped after
well-known open algorithms. Exact third-party shader ports must preserve
upstream headers and add per-file attribution here before import.

Planned attributions before exact shader integration:

- AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution 1.0 EASU + RCAS, MIT.
  Local Crisp shaders are derived from ffx_fsr1.h, version v1.20210629:
  https://github.com/GPUOpen-Effects/FidelityFX-FSR/blob/master/ffx-fsr/ffx_fsr1.h
- AMD Contrast Adaptive Sharpening, MIT.
- Anime4K v4 from bloc97/Anime4K, MIT.
- ArtCNN from Artoriuz/ArtCNN, MIT. Verified source target:
  https://github.com/Artoriuz/ArtCNN at commit b2fb535f3446060f9cb1782937f46385ea6cacc5.
  Local file `src/upscaler/modes/neural-lite/artcnn-c4f16-preview.wgsl`
  is a non-production staging shader written for this project. It contains no
  copied ArtCNN weights; the real port must preserve upstream shader headers
  before Neural-Lite is enabled.
- RAVU shader variants from bjin/mpv-prescalers, LGPL-3.0-or-later.
  Planned sources pinned at commit b3f0a59d68f33b7162051ea5970a5169558f0ea2:
  ravu-zoom-ar-r3.hook and ravu-lite-ar-r3.hook.
